AttributeList.Text:
============================================================================ This module is generates an alarm regarding a light curtain. The module manages also the bypass key and the pollution alarm. The light curtain alarm is reset by means of the AlarmResetPB signal.
This module generates also a word containing all necessary information for HMI Icon animation, and a word with all information for HMI safety module diagnostic screen. ============================================================================
